  "prompt": "Top 10 website makers?",
  "response": "Here\u2019s a list of the **top 10 website builders** in 2023, based on features, ease of use, flexibility, and value for money:\n\n---\n\n### **1. Wix**\n- **Best for:** Beginners and small businesses.\n- **Key Features:** Drag-and-drop editor, 800+ templates, AI-powered tools, and a free plan.\n- **Pricing:** Free plan available; paid plans start at $16/month.\n\n---\n\n### **2. Squarespace**\n- **Best for:** Creatives and visually stunning websites.\n- **Key Features:** Elegant designs, blogging tools, e-commerce capabilities, and mobile optimization.\n- **Pricing:** Starts at $16/month.\n\n---\n\n### **3. Shopify**\n- **Best for:** E-commerce businesses.\n- **Key Features:** Robust online store tools, payment gateways, inventory management, and app integrations.\n- **Pricing:** Starts at $39/month.\n\n---\n\n### **4. WordPress (.org)**\n- **Best for:** Advanced users and custom websites.\n- **Key Features:** Open-source, highly customizable, thousands of plugins, and full control.\n- **Pricing:** Free (but requires hosting, themes, and plugins).\n\n---\n\n### **5. Weebly**\n- **Best for:** Small business websites.\n- **Key Features:** Drag-and-drop builder, e-commerce features, and responsive designs.\n- **Pricing:** Free plan available; paid plans start at $10/month.\n\n---\n\n### **6. Webflow**\n- **Best for:** Designers and developers.\n- **Key Features:** Advanced design tools, CMS capabilities, and hosting included.\n- **Pricing:** Starts at $14/month.\n\n---\n\n### **7. GoDaddy Website Builder**\n- **Best for:** Quick and simple websites.\n- **Key Features:** Easy-to-use, AI-assisted design, and affordable pricing.\n- **Pricing:** Starts at $9.99/month.\n\n---\n\n### **8. Zyro**\n- **Best for:** Budget-friendly websites.\n- **Key Features:** AI tools, drag-and-drop editor, and fast load times.\n- **Pricing:** Starts at $2.90/month.\n\n---\n\n### **9. Duda**\n- **Best for:** Agencies and multi-site management.\n- **Key Features:** Team collaboration, responsive designs, and client management tools.\n- **Pricing:** Starts at $14/month.\n\n---\n\n### **10. Elementor (for WordPress)**\n- **Best for:** WordPress users who want more design flexibility.\n- **Key Features:** Drag-and-drop editor, pre-designed templates, and integrations.\n- **Pricing:** Free basic plan; Pro starts at $49/year.\n\n---\n\n### **How to Choose the Right Website Builder**\n- **For Beginners:** Wix, Squarespace, or Weebly are great starting points.\n- **For E-commerce:** Shopify or Squarespace are top choices.\n- **For Customization:** WordPress.org or Webflow offer the most flexibility.\n- **For Budget-Friendly Options:** Zyro or Weebly are cost-effective.\n\nLet me know if you\u2019d like more details about any of these! \ud83d\ude80",
  "temperature": 1.0,
